Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（歡迎來到伊勢）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞希子小姐  你搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是去了下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說多少次你才會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我只是稍微去散了會步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熄燈之後馬上就溜出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才  才沒有那種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有乖乖地去睡覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是有在乖乖睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的大包包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因為身體稍微好了一點就到處亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心讓你永遠出不了院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再偷溜出去就讓你全裸跳盂蘭盆舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意吧  這樣太淒涼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意跳裸舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不願意跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就好好聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有女孩子在這裡住院的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看到的話超丟臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你摸我的臀部了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  亞希子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條走廊太窄不小心碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這色老頭  一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在懷疑我這個病入膏肓的老人家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  好過分的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別只在這種時候拿出一副病人的嘴臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟跳得厲害  血壓…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言  去死吧  臭老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛  只是跳裸舞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小司不知道亞希子小姐的本性才笑得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找架打嗎？正好老娘手癢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的可怕之處就是說到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天裸體跳舞的話會感冒的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  戎崎的肝炎本來就是類似感冒的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡一覺就會好了的啦  稍微跳一下沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你這麼一說真是一肚子的火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這些饅頭是送給我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘎吱嘎吱吃個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戎崎也吃點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  山西說的是實話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是兩三個月不運動  一直睡著就會好的病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病名是急性肝炎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然似乎是病毒性的病症
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住了一個月的院後好了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所事事 閒得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內科的田中醫生  內科的田中醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立即前往護士站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新來一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好意思說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是三天前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從縣外的醫院轉院過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋庭里香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你同樣是十七歲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她身體這麼差嗎  要住在東病院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼  亞希子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓你偷跑出去的非常措施
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想上廁所的話怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:05:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  來真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也開始了  廣瀨義一的秩序料理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了哦  這裡才是關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加今日五時防災訓練的職員請於接待處集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加今日五時防災訓練的職員請於接待處集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這種感覺真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要得意忘形了  你還未成年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這點誘惑都無法抗拒的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我會復仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個小城市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中畢業後準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是去上東京或者名古屋的學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會離開這個城市嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正有此打算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人羨慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞希子小姐也離開不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  話雖然是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實行起來卻意外地困難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  那張長椅  要不要幫你移開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  有條件的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能成為里香的傾訴對像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香？那個秋庭里香？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有一些任性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川龍之介  她是他的忠實讀者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴她你也是芥川龍之介的忠實讀者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是幫你移開長椅的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午  午安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谷崎小姐說的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷崎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說亞希子小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經讀了這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡這裡面的「蜜橘」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然既短又樸素
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻是很好的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好呢  「蜜橘」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的有讀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你初次來這地方嗎  我聽亞希子小姐說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是什麼都沒有的鄉下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有伊勢神宮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我說的是神宮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只是個小地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以從那扇窗戶往外看  一切都盡收眼底
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所在的學校以及圖書館都看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家在那炮台山的對面  所以看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮台山？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為過去那上面有座炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以本地人都這麼叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞希子小姐說有共同話題會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  並不是說想故意欺騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為幫我找到了在尋找的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借到書了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看的才不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該吩咐過絕對不要把這個借來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這麼一點事情都辦不好  真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去借一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天外面很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過無論我吩咐什麼都會聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  這就去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快一點的話圖書館要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡量快一點去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論我吩咐什麼都要聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我說了想要  你就要幫我拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想笑一笑  你就要逗我開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能做到的話  我就原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書借來了  這次沒錯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我放在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又偷偷溜出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去了朋友那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了你這個年紀的話必須要多多進攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人家給你見識一下賭上住院生涯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易收集到的珍藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下  下次再看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來  陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術室是這種感覺的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太好吧  他們會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一  躺下去試試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  手術開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你手裡拿著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:13:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫沒問題  相信你什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍  等  一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在裡面？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  剛才的確有聽到人的聲音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一好奇怪  臉都扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現的話絕對會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身體怎麼了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:15:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說東病院裡住的都是重病患者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然非常嚴重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…大概會死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟的瓣膜知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡無法正常工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要治好只有移植
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是我的組織很脆弱  失敗的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也因為同樣的病作過手術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在手術的途中…心臟停止了跳動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要做手術的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須做好可能會和爸爸一樣的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一你告訴我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山叫做炮台山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在手術之前  爸爸帶我去過那座山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然本來不可以登山的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是勉強帶我上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定是做好了覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候雖然不知道那是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但爸爸說過那座山叫做炮台山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  一直望著窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望著那座山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再去那裡一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  我也能做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天快亮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  小司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多田先生怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:17:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病情急速惡化  去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有東西要交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多田先生曾恢復過一次意識
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為他要說什麼重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻是要把這些A書全交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當作是遺囑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  用心好好收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想…要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前你父親帶你去過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次由我帶你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我去  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑  斑馬假面！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一不用管我  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道之後會有什麼下場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小司  你真是設想周到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸把我抱起來  站在了上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:21:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也是懷著這種心情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也是在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這樣幫我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸說過了  要好好珍惜女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是會說話的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經又嗜酒又賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差勁透了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前就死了  喝酒喝壞了身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  所以把我帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一也一樣
